# Review Trigger

> Full context verification to prevent staleness and maintain accuracy.

---

## `/review` ‚Äî Full Context Verification

When the user types **`/review`**, systematically walk through all private/ context files to verify accuracy and update timestamps.

### When to Use
- Weekly (standalone or as part of `/weekly`)
- After a break from using the system (>3 days)
- Before high-stakes meetings where context accuracy matters
- When onboarding a new LLM conversation

---

